  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Droplets are utility and infiltration. They slip under doors, into sealed containers, through arrow slits. They can confirm whether a cistern is the water supply for a building, whether a moat is deep, or whether something is already living in a well. Their combat contribution is negligible. A summoner who understands what a Droplet actually is will find it useful in ways that have nothing to do with fighting.</p>"
