    "sensesNotes": "Darkvision 60 ft, Blindsight 10 ft (in water only)",
    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Splash [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 3 + Ranged Combat 1), Range: 10 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 1 damage; target gains Dazzled condition until end of their next turn from water in the eyes</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 2 damage + 2 cold damage (Half DR); target makes Reflex save (1 success) or drops a loosely held item from the wet grip</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Aqueous Form:</strong> Fits through any gap water can pass through. An undisturbed Droplet in clear water requires a Hard task Perception check (2 successes) to notice by sight.</li>\n<li><strong>Contaminate:</strong> Over 1 minute of contact, makes a body of liquid foul-tasting, cloudy, or cold. Not harmful but detectable with a Perception or Medicine check (1 success).</li>\n</ul>",
